From now on :



This journal is friends only. If you comment, and I know you, you will be added. If I don't know you, get to know me a little better and I will also consider adding you. Yes, I'm antisocial. Deal with it
I will not just add any random person that comes along. If I don't know you, you won't be added and that's it. I do not see the point in having a friends only LJ if I'm just going to add any random idiot that asks.
